OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK to scrap golden visa    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fscheme for foreign         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Finvestors                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Visas offering foreign investors       
OL,6, fast-track residency in the UK are     
OL,7, expected to be scrapped by the         
OL,8, government, amid pressure over UK links
OL,9, to Russia.                             
OL,11,FA government source confirmed reports  
OL,12,Fof an announcement next week on Tier 1 
OL,13,Finvestor visas, which offer residency  
OL,14,Fto those spending at least #2m.        
OL,16,FThe scheme was introduced in 2008 to   
OL,17,Fencourage wealthy people from outside  
OL,18,Fthe EU to invest in the UK.            
OL,20,FIt has been under review for some time,
OL,21,Fafter concerns it is open to abuse.    
